Package: SNPstats
Type: Package
Title: SNP Statistics for Genetic Epidemiology
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-10
Authors@R: person("Victor", "Moreno", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "v.moreno@iconcologia.net")
Description: Performs SNP analysis for genetic epidemiology studies. Computes allele and genotype 
    frequencies, Hardy-Weinberg equilibrium tests, SNP-response association, linkage disequilibrium, 
    and haplotype analysis. Based on the SNPstats web tool (https://www.snpstats.net).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: genetics, haplo.stats
Imports: 
    jmvcore (>= 1.2.0),
    R6,
    genetics,
    haplo.stats
References: 
    Sole X, Guino E, Valls J, Iniesta R, Moreno V (2006). SNPStats: a web tool for the analysis of association studies. <em>Bioinformatics</em> 22(15):1928–1929.
